description:
AnrFunctionEUtran: Table containing configuration parameters for E-UTRAN (Evolved Universal Terrestrial Radio Access Network) ANR (Advanced Network Reconstruction) function.

dateTime: Timestamp of the configuration data.
Area_Name: Name of the geographic area.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier (likely a duplicate of CellId).
Id3:  Generic identifier (purpose unclear from data).
Id4: Generic identifier (purpose unclear from data).
vsDataType: Type of data, specifying it is related to ANR function in E-UTRAN.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format, Ericsson specific.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrCgiMeasEUtranEnabled: Flag indicating whether E-UTRAN CGI measurement is enabled.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrFunctionEUtranId: Unique ID for the ANR function in E-UTRAN.
AnrFunctionEUtran.x2SetupPolicy: Policy for X2 interface setup.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrEutranInterFMeasReportMax: Maximum number of inter-frequency measurement reports for E-UTRAN.
AnrFunctionEUtran.hoAllowedEutranPolicy: Policy for handover to E-UTRAN.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesEUtraIntraFDecr:  Decrement value for intra-frequency UE threshold.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesThreshInterFMin: Minimum inter-frequency UE threshold.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrIntraFreqState: Status of intra-frequency ANR.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrInterFreqState: Status of inter-frequency ANR.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesEUtraIntraFIncrAnr: Increment value for intra-frequency UE threshold for ANR.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrEutranInterFMeasReportIncr: Increment value for inter-frequency measurement reports for E-UTRAN.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesEUtraIntraFMax: Maximum value for intra-frequency UE threshold.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrEutranInterFMeasReportDecr: Decrement value for inter-frequency measurement reports for E-UTRAN.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesThreshInterFIncrAnr: Increment value for inter-frequency UE threshold for ANR.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesThreshInterFMax: Maximum inter-frequency UE threshold.
AnrFunctionEUtran.cellAddRsrpThresholdEutran: RSRP (Reference Signal Received Power) threshold for cell addition in E-UTRAN.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesEUtraIntraFIncrHo: Increment value for intra-frequency UE threshold for handover.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrEutranInterFMeasReportMin: Minimum number of inter-frequency measurement reports for E-UTRAN.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesEUtraIntraFMin: Minimum value for intra-frequency UE threshold.
AnrFunctionEUtran.acquirePlmnIdListEnabled: Flag indicating whether PLMN ID list acquisition is enabled.
AnrFunctionEUtran.lbCellOffloadCapacityPolicy: Policy for load balancing cell offload capacity.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesThreshInterFIncrHo: Increment value for inter-frequency UE threshold for handover.
AnrFunctionEUtran.cellAddRsrqThresholdEutran: RSRQ (Reference Signal Received Quality) threshold for cell addition in E-UTRAN.
AnrFunctionEUtran.anrUesThreshInterFDecr: Decrement value for inter-frequency UE threshold.
